      <abstract>
        <p>P&amp;F Industries board authorizes repurchase of up to 180,000 shares of common stocks over next 12 months (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The board of P&amp;F Industries Inc. of Farmingdale (Nasdaq: PFIN) authorized the repurchase of up to 180,000 shares of common stock over the next twelve months. P&amp;F makes and imports air-powered tools, hydraulic cylinders, baseboard and radiant-heating products, security hardware, compressor air filters, pipe-cutting and threading tools and heavy-duty pipe wrenches.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
